Kim Jong-un attends the Arirang Festival performance in Pyongyang with his father Kim Jong-il. It is Kim Jong-un's first appearance before the world's media. (BBC) Senior Chinese leader Zhou Yongkang is also in attendance. (Xinhua)North Korean television broadcasts live a military parade for Supreme Leader Kim Jong-il and his heir apparent Kim Jong-un. (AP via Google News) (BBC) (Arirang)